off is reach, right?

00:05:42.240 --> 00:05:46.690
I mean, a lot of developers,
when you're executing in code

00:05:46.690 --> 00:05:49.630
in the PC space you have a
certain number of digital

00:05:49.630 --> 00:05:54.510
distribution silos that
you're locked into.

00:05:54.510 --> 00:05:57.260
