the digital distribution age

00:05:57.260 --> 00:06:00.350
of games right now is really
just a one-off from where we

00:06:00.350 --> 00:06:02.960
were a few years ago in
the retail market.

00:06:02.960 --> 00:06:05.580
Where effectively, developers
spent a lot of time scrapping

00:06:05.580 --> 00:06:09.690
and fighting for market share
and visibility and eyeballs.

00:06:09.690 --> 00:06:11.640
