tons and tons of time fighting

00:06:15.680 --> 00:06:18.080
for small pieces of user
attention in these larger

00:06:18.080 --> 00:06:19.980
digital distribution
ecosystems.

00:06:19.980 --> 00:06:21.370
The web fixes that.

00:06:21.370 --> 00:06:24.460
The web isn't about a single
digital distribution silo,

00:06:24.460 --> 00:06:26.900
